snippet.title: James Cameron's AVATAR: The Game - Official Launch Trailer | HD
snippet.description:
James Cameron's AVATAR: The Game - Official Launch Trailer | HD
Developer: Ubisoft
Release: Dec 3, 2009.
Genre: Action, Adventure
Platform: PS3, Xbox 360, PC
Publisher: Ubisoft
Website: http://www.ubisoft.com/
